## 4.4 Crosswalk Kontrol – Evidence – Metrics

| Area        | Kontrol                               | Evidence (Bukti)                        | Metrics                          |
|-------------|---------------------------------------|-----------------------------------------|----------------------------------|
| Governance  | Kebijakan AI Governance                | Dokumen kebijakan, persetujuan manajemen | # kebijakan yang diadopsi        |
| Risk        | Risk Register AI                      | Risk log, matriks risiko                 | % risiko dengan mitigasi aktif   |
| Controls    | PII Redaction, Explainability         | Log redaksi PII, laporan model explain   | % akurasi + % PII terlindungi    |
| Lifecycle   | Model Registry & Monitoring           | Model card, audit trail                  | # model teregistrasi & dimonitor |
| Compliance  | Regulatory Alignment (UU PDP, POJK)   | AIA, DPIA, dokumen compliance            | Jumlah kontrol selaras regulasi  |
